  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 triggered)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; the 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor is recorded as not-assessed on the grounds that its scope does not apply to this COU — however, the correct encoding for a genuinely out-of-scope factor would be 'not-applicable', not 'not-assessed'. At MRL 3 the absence of a formal assessment for this factor materially weakens the credibility argument (W-EP-04). Decision is recorded as Accepted, masking the epistemic gap.",
